videos.headline: Georgia Tech airs it out for 59-yard TD
videos.description: Georgia Tech gets the first score of the game as QB James Graham goes deep to find Ahmarean Brown for a 59-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Georgia Tech's Carter makes acrobatic grab in end zone
videos.description: Georgia Tech QB James Graham lofts a pass to the end zone and Malachi Carter adjusts to make the 25-yard touchdown catch.
